### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "identifier": "super-admin-1",
    "password": "super-admin-1"
}

### Registrasi
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "tamu-saja",
    "email": "tamu-saja@gmail.com",
    "password": "tamu-saja"
}

